## ğŸ”§ Customization

The application is designed to be easily customizable:

### Enabling Real-Time Processing
Uncomment line 398 in the JavaScript section to enable automatic Base64 detection:
```javascript
enableRealTime(); // Uncomment this line
```

### Color Scheme Modification
Update the CSS custom properties to change the color scheme:
```css
.btn-encode { background: #your-color; }
.btn-decode { background: #your-color; }
.btn-copy { background: #your-color; }
.btn-clear { background: #your-color; }
```

### Text Area Sizing
Modify the `.text-area` class to adjust input/output area sizes:
```css
.text-area {
    min-height: 300px; /* Adjust height */
}
```

